1
00:02:08,100 --> 00:02:13,340
Eternal Love of Dream

2
00:02:14,180 --> 00:02:16,620
Episode 28

3
00:02:19,340 --> 00:02:19,940
Your Majesty,

4
00:02:21,420 --> 00:02:23,460
has the war of Mount Fuyu not finished yet?

5
00:02:24,660 --> 00:02:26,020
That Demon Lord Yan

6
00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:27,980
is not a threat.

7
00:02:28,460 --> 00:02:29,260
Now that the disaster is quelled,

8
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:31,220
Your Majesty, why are you still so worried?

9
00:02:32,540 --> 00:02:33,900
I left her in the Fanyin Valley.

10
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:36,580
What have you left?

11
00:02:37,220 --> 00:02:38,220
A silk handkerchief.

12
00:02:41,740 --> 00:02:42,300
Leave me alone.

13
00:02:43,100 --> 00:02:43,540
Yes.

14
00:02:58,340 --> 00:02:59,660
Which man in the world

15
00:02:59,700 --> 00:03:01,140
doesn't like Ji Heng?

16
00:03:04,820 --> 00:03:06,340
In that case,

17
00:03:06,940 --> 00:03:08,580
since His Majesty likes Ji Heng so much,

18
00:03:08,700 --> 00:03:09,940
why did I hear that

19
00:03:09,940 --> 00:03:12,100
when they got out of the Ten-evil Lotus Land,

20
00:03:12,300 --> 00:03:13,740
Ji Heng asked His Majesty for a spiritual fox

21
00:03:13,740 --> 00:03:15,220
they found together,

22
00:03:15,540 --> 00:03:17,180
but His Majesty didn't give it to her?

23
00:03:18,140 --> 00:03:19,100
What do you know?

24
00:03:19,500 --> 00:03:20,700
It's a strategy.

25
00:03:21,180 --> 00:03:22,380
It's just like you like ice face,

26
00:03:22,500 --> 00:03:24,780
so you will try every means to connect with him.

27
00:03:26,980 --> 00:03:28,860
He didn't give that spiritual fox

28
00:03:29,020 --> 00:03:29,980
to Ji Heng

29
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:31,380
so that Ji Heng would visit Tai Chen Palace

30
00:03:31,420 --> 00:03:33,420
frequently to see it later.

31
00:03:33,900 --> 00:03:35,860
He's really cunning.

32
00:03:37,620 --> 00:03:39,460
Though he talks casually,

33
00:03:39,980 --> 00:03:41,300
he's pretty scrupulous.

34
00:03:43,700 --> 00:03:44,940
I know you like him,

35
00:03:45,220 --> 00:03:46,740
just as I like Ji Heng.

36
00:03:47,460 --> 00:03:48,660
We have the same misfortune.

37
00:03:48,940 --> 00:03:49,740
Take my advice.

38
00:03:50,100 --> 00:03:51,740
It's never too late to mend your ways.

39
00:03:55,220 --> 00:03:56,100
I don't know this sentence

40
00:03:56,100 --> 00:03:57,380
can also be interpreted this way.

41
00:03:58,340 --> 00:03:59,980
Just mend your ways.

42
00:04:02,460 --> 00:04:04,260
However, the ice face failed to get married in the end.

43
00:04:04,420 --> 00:04:05,420
Ji Heng ran away from the wedding.

44
00:04:06,460 --> 00:04:07,700
He lost not only his empress

45
00:04:07,860 --> 00:04:08,900
but also the spiritual fox.

46
00:04:09,020 --> 00:04:11,580
How miserable he was!

47
00:04:17,420 --> 00:04:18,580
You said you're from Qingqiu.

48
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:19,820
Do you know

49
00:04:19,940 --> 00:04:20,900
where that spiritual fox is now?

50
00:04:23,180 --> 00:04:24,420
It sounds ridiculous.

51
00:04:24,860 --> 00:04:26,820
The ice face actually

52
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:27,900
came to me for the fox.

53
00:04:27,940 --> 00:04:29,940
He thought I had abducted the fox.

54
00:04:30,220 --> 00:04:31,660
Do I look like someone

55
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:32,620
who would abduct a fox?

56
00:04:32,740 --> 00:04:34,260
He really underestimated me!

57
00:04:35,340 --> 00:04:35,940
However,

58
00:04:36,460 --> 00:04:38,540
I heard that he still hasn't found it after years of searching.

59
00:04:39,780 --> 00:04:40,420
In my opinion,

60
00:04:40,540 --> 00:04:42,820
that fox is probably dead.

61
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:45,700
I wonder what kind of a fox that is

62
00:04:46,220 --> 00:04:47,260
to be so favored by him.

63
00:04:49,180 --> 00:04:50,300
Warrior Yan,

64
00:04:50,780 --> 00:04:51,660
after talking for so long,

65
00:04:51,780 --> 00:04:52,940
you must be thirsty.

66
00:04:53,420 --> 00:04:54,980
Shall we look for the exit?

67
00:04:55,260 --> 00:04:56,300
We can't stay here

68
00:04:56,380 --> 00:04:57,420
forever.

69
00:04:59,100 --> 00:04:59,620
You've made a point.

70
00:05:26,300 --> 00:05:26,740
Watch out!

71
00:05:33,340 --> 00:05:34,380
After all, we've been through trouble together.

72
00:05:34,500 --> 00:05:35,500
I can't watch you fall down

73
00:05:35,540 --> 00:05:36,380
and do nothing.

74
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:37,420
Forget it! I'm coming!

75
00:05:56,780 --> 00:05:58,140
Today is really an auspicious day.

76
00:05:58,420 --> 00:05:59,980
It's exceptionally easy to avoid those spies

77
00:06:00,100 --> 00:06:01,100
in the imperial palace and get outside.

78
00:06:06,900 --> 00:06:07,180
Let's go and have a look!

79
00:06:07,180 --> 00:06:07,700
What's wrong?

80
00:06:07,900 --> 00:06:08,220
Look over there!

81
00:06:09,220 --> 00:06:09,980
Turn them over!

82
00:06:14,420 --> 00:06:15,220
They hit someone.

83
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:20,220
Second Prince!

84
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:22,700
I pay respects to Your Highness!

85
00:06:30,860 --> 00:06:32,020
How dare you!

86
00:06:32,860 --> 00:06:35,180
You actually attacked
the Second Prince of the inseparable king bird!

87
00:06:35,780 --> 00:06:36,900
I'm so unlucky

88
00:06:37,540 --> 00:06:39,260
to have fallen into the nest of the inseparable king birds!

89
00:06:40,020 --> 00:06:42,100
The inseparable king birds had a problem with Qingqiu.

90
00:06:42,260 --> 00:06:43,180
I can't let them know

91
00:06:43,300 --> 00:06:44,260
I'm from Qingqiu.

92
00:06:52,740 --> 00:06:55,860
It seems that without suffering,

93
00:06:56,540 --> 00:06:57,260
you won't know

94
00:06:57,340 --> 00:06:59,100
how powerful we inseparable king birds are.

95
00:06:59,660 --> 00:07:00,100
Guards!

96
00:07:00,420 --> 00:07:01,260
Take them to the prison

97
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:02,180
to wait for execution!

98
00:07:02,620 --> 00:07:03,220
- Yes! - Yes!

99
00:07:07,620 --> 00:07:07,940
Go!

100
00:07:12,780 --> 00:07:14,860
That girl

101
00:07:14,980 --> 00:07:16,620
looks familiar.

102
00:07:35,740 --> 00:07:38,300
Brother, you finally wake up!

103
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:40,420
You freaked me out.

104
00:07:46,700 --> 00:07:47,580
Are you OK?

105
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:50,140
Brother, what're you doing?

106
00:07:53,580 --> 00:07:54,100
Brother,

107
00:07:54,660 --> 00:07:55,820
where are you going?

108
00:07:56,860 --> 00:07:58,340
You were knocked out a moment ago.

109
00:07:58,700 --> 00:08:01,380
The pharmacist said you should rest well.

110
00:08:04,820 --> 00:08:05,460
Jielu,

111
00:08:06,260 --> 00:08:08,580
you said I was knocked out?

112
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:09,380
Right!

113
00:08:09,660 --> 00:08:11,660
And you were knocked out by two people.

114
00:08:13,140 --> 00:08:14,700
Is my secret trip outside

115
00:08:14,900 --> 00:08:15,860
the imperial palace exposed?

116
00:08:16,140 --> 00:08:17,500
That I haven't heard of.

117
00:08:18,060 --> 00:08:19,820
However, for us inseparable king birds,

118
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:22,340
traditionally, unmarried men
are not allowed to leave the valley alone.

119
00:08:22,660 --> 00:08:25,180
Brother, why do you break the rule repeatedly?

120
00:08:27,220 --> 00:08:28,700
You know that I've longed for

121
00:08:28,860 --> 00:08:29,940
the colorful world outside the valley

122
00:08:30,420 --> 00:08:32,060
and wanted to experience the outside world for a long time.

123
00:08:32,980 --> 00:08:34,900
I've waited so long for the Jiazi Valley to open,

124
00:08:35,980 --> 00:08:37,060
but now it's all ruined.

125
00:08:37,100 --> 00:08:37,420
If...

126
00:08:38,380 --> 00:08:39,980
If Her Majesty finds out...

127
00:08:40,460 --> 00:08:40,660
Well...

128
00:08:40,820 --> 00:08:41,620
So...

129
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:45,460
So I sneaked out.

130
00:08:46,620 --> 00:08:47,020
Well,

131
00:08:47,700 --> 00:08:50,380
where are the two people who knocked me out?

132
00:08:50,700 --> 00:08:52,660
After hearing that they knocked you out,

133
00:08:52,860 --> 00:08:54,820
Her Majesty ordered to put them into prison.

134
00:08:57,620 --> 00:08:59,300
Just let me finish.

135
00:09:00,620 --> 00:09:01,860
Luckily, you're not severely injured,

136
00:09:02,020 --> 00:09:04,220
so they've been sent to the water dungeon instead.

137
00:09:04,420 --> 00:09:05,500
I was the one who made the mistake.

138
00:09:05,660 --> 00:09:07,060
I certainly can't get them in trouble.

139
00:09:08,020 --> 00:09:10,140
Jielu, do you who knocked me out?

140
00:09:11,140 --> 00:09:12,540
I only know it's a man and a woman.

141
00:09:14,100 --> 00:09:14,820
Brother,

142
00:09:15,060 --> 00:09:16,420
wait for me!

143
00:09:39,820 --> 00:09:40,260
Get out!

144
00:09:48,420 --> 00:09:50,060
Where're you taking me?

145
00:09:50,420 --> 00:09:50,940
The water dungeon.

146
00:09:51,380 --> 00:09:52,180
The water dungeon?

147
00:09:52,860 --> 00:09:54,780
You birds do have many tricks.

148
00:09:55,220 --> 00:09:55,900
Cut the crap!

149
00:09:56,980 --> 00:09:58,940
Still feeling dizzy after falling down just now,

150
00:09:59,060 --> 00:09:59,940
I don't feel like having a fight.

151
00:10:00,460 --> 00:10:02,260
Otherwise, you wouldn't be able to capture me.

152
00:10:04,180 --> 00:10:06,300
Knocking out the prince of the inseparable king birds

153
00:10:06,380 --> 00:10:07,620
can either be big or small.

154
00:10:07,980 --> 00:10:09,180
If he can't wake up,

155
00:10:09,300 --> 00:10:10,260
it's a big deal.

156
00:10:10,660 --> 00:10:11,580
If he wakes up,

157
00:10:11,580 --> 00:10:12,620
with others interceding for us,

158
00:10:12,820 --> 00:10:14,340
there's hope.

159
00:10:15,380 --> 00:10:15,940
Hurry up! Hurry up!

160
00:10:23,020 --> 00:10:23,580
Her Majesty ordered

161
00:10:23,820 --> 00:10:25,420
to escort them to the Palace Hall immediately.

162
00:10:27,340 --> 00:10:28,780
It seems that he has woken up.

163
00:10:38,740 --> 00:10:40,900
I just heard from the Second Prince that

164
00:10:41,300 --> 00:10:43,220
you're the prince and princess of

165
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:45,500
the night owls across the river.

166
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:49,340
Admiring the Imperial College of our clan,

167
00:10:49,580 --> 00:10:51,300
you took a study tour here.

168
00:10:51,940 --> 00:10:53,780
You injured the Second Prince by accident.

169
00:11:00,700 --> 00:11:03,260
Why did the Second Prince make up such a lie?

170
00:11:04,260 --> 00:11:06,820
It appears that it's a misunderstanding after all.

171
00:11:07,020 --> 00:11:08,620
Sorry for making you suffer.

172
00:11:09,340 --> 00:11:11,380
You're honored guests coming from afar.

173
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:12,340
Well,

174
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:14,460
we should treat you well.

175
00:11:15,020 --> 00:11:15,700
Thank you, Your Majesty!

176
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:18,660
Thank you, Your Majesty!

177
00:11:19,420 --> 00:11:22,500
Since you admire our Imperial College,

178
00:11:23,140 --> 00:11:24,940
I'll allow you to live in the Jifeng Courtyard of

179
00:11:25,140 --> 00:11:27,180
the Imperial College.

180
00:11:28,260 --> 00:11:30,180
On the one hand, your sincere wish

181
00:11:30,220 --> 00:11:32,060
to study in the Imperial College can be satisfied.

182
00:11:32,660 --> 00:11:35,260
On the other hand, it's convenient
for younger generations of our two clans

183
00:11:35,380 --> 00:11:36,660
to exchange and compete with each other.

184
00:11:37,260 --> 00:11:38,900
What do you think?

185
00:11:39,260 --> 00:11:41,420
Your Majesty, thank you for your careful
and considerate arrangement.

186
00:11:41,620 --> 00:11:43,060
We can't thank you enough.

187
00:11:43,180 --> 00:11:44,780
We'll definitely study hard in the Imperial College.

188
00:11:52,620 --> 00:11:53,180
Mother,

189
00:11:54,380 --> 00:11:56,620
then I'll take them to the Jifeng Courtyard.

190
00:11:57,100 --> 00:11:57,700
Go ahead.

191
00:11:59,500 --> 00:11:59,820
Please.

192
00:12:07,820 --> 00:12:08,500
Let's go!

193
00:12:09,700 --> 00:12:10,100
Go!

194
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:35,340
Wait outside.

195
00:12:35,940 --> 00:12:36,340
Yes!

196
00:12:38,300 --> 00:12:40,500
Your Highness, thank you for saving us on the hall just now.

197
00:12:40,780 --> 00:12:42,860
But there's one thing we really can't understand.

198
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:44,100
Are you wondering

199
00:12:44,260 --> 00:12:45,740
why I saved you?

200
00:12:47,780 --> 00:12:48,420
Frankly speaking,

201
00:12:48,660 --> 00:12:50,940
it's also for my own good.

202
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:52,980
You mean?

203
00:12:54,340 --> 00:12:55,340
I went out of the valley without permission.

204
00:12:55,500 --> 00:12:56,660
If my mother finds out,

205
00:12:56,940 --> 00:12:58,060
she won't spare me easily.

206
00:12:58,660 --> 00:12:59,260
But now,

207
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:00,900
you're safe,

208
00:13:01,220 --> 00:13:02,500
and I can avoid being punished.

209
00:13:03,020 --> 00:13:04,940
Please keep the secret for me.

210
00:13:05,780 --> 00:13:06,780
Your Highness, rest assured.

211
00:13:07,340 --> 00:13:07,900
However,

212
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:09,660
when can we get out of the valley?

213
00:13:09,940 --> 00:13:11,900
I'm afraid you'll have to wait for another 60 years.

214
00:13:12,180 --> 00:13:13,060
60 years!

215
00:13:13,260 --> 00:13:14,300
It's so long!

216
00:13:14,820 --> 00:13:17,060
It's a long story.

217
00:13:18,420 --> 00:13:20,300
We inseparable king birds

218
00:13:20,420 --> 00:13:21,740
are born fragile and delicate.

219
00:13:22,660 --> 00:13:25,300
A tiny bit of foul air in the mortal realm can make us sick.

220
00:13:25,660 --> 00:13:26,100
Therefore,

221
00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:27,740
many years ago, our ancestors

222
00:13:27,900 --> 00:13:30,220
found the Fanyin Valley after untold hardships

223
00:13:30,380 --> 00:13:32,860
and led our entire clan to live a reclusive life in the valley.

224
00:13:33,460 --> 00:13:35,900
Does this have anything to do with us leaving the valley?

225
00:13:36,820 --> 00:13:37,460
Take it easy.

226
00:13:37,620 --> 00:13:38,660
I haven't finished yet.

227
00:13:39,180 --> 00:13:41,580
There's foul air sealed at the core of our valley.

228
00:13:41,900 --> 00:13:42,940
If we open the valley too often,

229
00:13:43,220 --> 00:13:44,540
the foul air might leak.

230
00:13:45,340 --> 00:13:46,540
Once the Fanyin Valley is polluted,

231
00:13:46,740 --> 00:13:48,780
the Four Seas and Eight Deserts will be in danger.

232
00:13:49,580 --> 00:13:51,940
So the Fanyin Valley only opens every 60 years,

233
00:13:52,380 --> 00:13:54,060
and it only opens a crack

234
00:13:54,420 --> 00:13:55,300
for a short period of time, so that

235
00:13:55,540 --> 00:13:57,020
immortal messengers from the Sky Kingdom

236
00:13:57,140 --> 00:13:58,420
on business to the valley can pass.

237
00:13:58,780 --> 00:14:01,700
The day you fell down
happens to be the opening date of the valley.

238
00:14:03,580 --> 00:14:04,100
Well,

239
00:14:04,260 --> 00:14:05,860
is there any other way to get out?

240
00:14:06,180 --> 00:14:08,740
Even the most perceptive immortal messenger from heaven

241
00:14:09,940 --> 00:14:11,020
needs to practice for three thousand years

242
00:14:11,340 --> 00:14:13,020
to pass that crack.

243
00:14:15,260 --> 00:14:15,940
So long...

244
00:14:16,980 --> 00:14:18,060
Take it easy.

245
00:14:18,460 --> 00:14:20,820
Fate had us meet each other this way.

246
00:14:21,420 --> 00:14:22,380
I'm Xiang Limeng.

247
00:14:22,740 --> 00:14:24,780
I wonder what your names are.

248
00:14:25,740 --> 00:14:26,980
You can call me Xiaojiu.

249
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:28,620
Xiaojiu?

250
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:29,540
Terrific!

251
00:14:30,220 --> 00:14:31,900
The princess of the night owls whose identity you've borrowed

252
00:14:32,100 --> 00:14:33,060
also has "Jiu" in her name.

253
00:14:33,220 --> 00:14:33,980
She's named Jiuge.

254
00:14:34,420 --> 00:14:36,740
It'll be convenient for you

255
00:14:36,860 --> 00:14:37,620
to use her name in the Fanyin Valley later.

256
00:14:38,180 --> 00:14:39,780
Then I'll call you Jiuge.

257
00:14:39,980 --> 00:14:41,300
OK! Good!

258
00:14:42,020 --> 00:14:44,220
The Jifeng Courtyard has two rooms,
the east room and the west room.

259
00:14:44,660 --> 00:14:45,900
Feel relieved to live here.

260
00:14:46,060 --> 00:14:48,100
Whatever you need, just tell the servants.

261
00:14:48,660 --> 00:14:50,180
Your Highness, you're really considerate.

262
00:14:50,660 --> 00:14:51,780
Just call me Meng.

263
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:55,740
Bro, I wonder how I should address you.

264
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:00,540
Warrior Yan!

265
00:15:03,860 --> 00:15:05,420
Just call me Yan.

266
00:15:05,780 --> 00:15:06,900
Jiuge. Yan.

267
00:15:07,260 --> 00:15:08,460
Have a good rest then.

268
00:15:08,820 --> 00:15:10,460
I'm leaving.

269
00:15:13,820 --> 00:15:15,100
I'll take the east room.

270
00:15:15,420 --> 00:15:16,540
You can have the west room.

271
00:15:20,140 --> 00:15:20,940
It's weird.

272
00:15:21,540 --> 00:15:22,820
After entering the Fanyin Valley,

273
00:15:22,940 --> 00:15:24,060
he seems infatuated.

274
00:15:24,420 --> 00:15:25,300
What's wrong with him?

275
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:41,540
Get up!

276
00:15:42,740 --> 00:15:43,700
What's wrong with you?

277
00:15:43,860 --> 00:15:44,980
Get up now!

278
00:15:45,740 --> 00:15:47,220
It's late at night! Why should I get up

279
00:15:47,380 --> 00:15:48,380
instead of sleeping?

280
00:15:48,500 --> 00:15:49,500
We've been trapped in the valley

281
00:15:49,620 --> 00:15:51,140
for so long.

282
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:52,340
Rather than sit here and wait,

283
